Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.33,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Einar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.43,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.44,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,I could ask you the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.44,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Why're you attackin' that tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.94,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,You tryna crush the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.74,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Are you gonna be a woodcutter, Einar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.04,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.80,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,I'm training for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.20,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Behold my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.03,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,You're a big lad, \Nbut you'd be useless in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.53,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Get ready for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.08,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:00.22,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,You don't have to throw a knife at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.75,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,You're holding dishes and spoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.26,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,You wouldn't mind a dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:14.49,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,They say bears have to \Neat lots before winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.64,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:23.77,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,So, why are you trainin' again all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:21.69,top,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Thankya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.44,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Well, because I gotta protect this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.58,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,After it was all burnt to ashes, \Nit's finally been rebuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.82,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,I'm not letting that happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.39,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,I'm sure Dad would—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.14,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Mister Guthmur's milk is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:54.14,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Right? That man knows his way around a teat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.40,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,What are you doin' \Nwith your hands? It's so creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.33,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.13,top,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.06,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.86,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Don't poke your nose into warrior stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:07.34,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Doesn't it frustrate you, \Nalways being on the losing side?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:10.96,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Dad died protecting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.08,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.00,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,And you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.63,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,You've rebuilt this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.36,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,and you're eating a delicious meal \Nwith two beautiful ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.33,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,We haven't lost at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:39.15,main,OLD MAN ON CART,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.61,main,OLD MAN VILLAGER,0,0,0,,Hey, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.58,main,CHILD VILLAGER,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:16.38,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Listen closely. Once we enter \Nthe woods, I want you to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.39,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Follow the river, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.27,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Lotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.53,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.91,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Don't think. Just run straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.58,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Your brother and I will be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.73,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.82,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,You ready? Let's get you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.01,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:44.99,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Einar, run. Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:45.91,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.92,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Come on. Stand, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.07,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.89,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.22,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.65,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Silly girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.16,main,VIKING B,0,0,0,,There are still people over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:15.08,main,VIKING C,0,0,0,,Hey, they've got women, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.10,main,VIKING B,0,0,0,,We're on our way, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.70,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Stand up, Einar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.52,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Take Lotta and go. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.53,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.63,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Even a dying old hag can still manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.88,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:55.08,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,As long as you're alive, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.56,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Ei...nar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.12,main,EMMA,0,0,0,,Lotta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.81,main,VIKING B,0,0,0,,Why aren't they running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.47,main,VIKING C,0,0,0,,Hey, she's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.63,main,VIKING D,0,0,0,,Your mom's dead, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.10,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Lotta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.35,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Let go! Einar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.10,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Lotta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.12,main,EINAR,0,0,0,,Let go of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.68,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Einar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.54,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.17,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,Einar! Einar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.41,main,LOTTA,0,0,0,,You'll pay for—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.30,main,VIKING C,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.35,main,VIKING B,0,0,0,,She freakin' stabbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.47,main,VIKING C,0,0,0,,Aw, man. What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.78,main,VIKING D,0,0,0,,Nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:29.48,main,VIKING D,0,0,0,,Let's sell the kid for beer money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.61,main,VIKING C,0,0,0,,You're such a dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.34,main,VIKING B,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:36.01,main,VIKING C,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go, beer money.
